{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/posts/2020-01-26---How-to-Write-A-Blog/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"294230f0-99b1-57d6-ab10-e62adfe9fce8","html":"<h1 id=\"why\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#why\" aria-label=\"why permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Why</h1>\n<p>This is the first section of a blog: <strong>Why</strong>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Why to write the blog?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For this doc, it's going to solve the problem:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>How to write a blog in the little bee playground?</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"what\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#what\" aria-label=\"what permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>What</h1>\n<p>This is the second section of a blog: <strong>What</strong>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>What's the solution?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>A blog in little bee playground should follows following rules:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>a blog should fill in basic contents with horizontal rule at the top.</li>\n<li>a blog should focus on solving a problem with three section: <code class=\"language-text\">why? What? How?</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"how\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how\" aria-label=\"how permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How</h1>\n<p>This is the second section of a blog: <strong>How</strong>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>How to implement the solution?</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"horizontal-rule\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#horizontal-rule\" aria-label=\"horizontal rule permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Horizontal Rule</h2>\n<p>Every blog should fill in <code class=\"language-text\">title</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">description</code> and so on with horizontal rule at the top.\nHere is an example:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">---\ntitle: &quot;This is the blog title&quot;\ncategory: &quot;category string&quot;\ntags:\n  - &quot;tag1&quot;\n  - &quot;tag2&quot;\ndescription: &quot;description...&quot;\n---</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">category</code> vs <code class=\"language-text\">tags</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>one blog only have one <code class=\"language-text\">category</code>, but several <code class=\"language-text\">tags</code>.</li>\n<li>little bee playground can group blogs with same <code class=\"language-text\">category</code> or same <code class=\"language-text\">tag</code> to users.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">category</code> is shown at the main page to users along with <code class=\"language-text\">title</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">description</code>, but <code class=\"language-text\">tags</code> can only bee seen inside the blog.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">title</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">description</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>they are shown at the main page as the index for blogs.</li>\n<li>it will be empty if a blog doesn't have <code class=\"language-text\">title</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">description</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"three-section\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#three-section\" aria-label=\"three section permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Three Section</h2>\n<p>Every blog in little bee playground should focus on solving a problem. And it should have three sections:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Why </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Why to write the blog? What's the problem?</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>What</p>\n<ul>\n<li>What's the solution in the blog?</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>How</p>\n<ul>\n<li>How to implement the solution?</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2020-01-26---How-to-Write-A-Blog/","tagSlugs":["/tag/blog/","/tag/intro/"]},"frontmatter":{"description":"This is a template for writing a blog in little bee playground.","tags":["Blog","Intro"],"title":"How to Write A Blog"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2020-01-26---How-to-Write-A-Blog/"}}}